trans-unit.source: Represents an extensibility element added to a <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref>, an <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.InputBinding"></xref> or an <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OutputBinding"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Rappresenta un elemento extensibility aggiunto a un <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"> </xref>, un <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.InputBinding"> </xref> o <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OutputBinding"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: It specifies the schema for XML messages that are not SOAP compliant.
trans-unit.target: Specifica lo schema per i messaggi XML che non sono compatibili con SOAP.
Questa classe non può essere ereditata.

trans-unit.source: For more information about specifying protocols for XML Web services, see [[\<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices>]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c).
trans-unit.target: Per ulteriori informazioni su come specificare i protocolli per i servizi Web XML, vedere [[\<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices >]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c).

trans-unit.source: For more information about Web Services Description Language (WSDL), see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
trans-unit.target: Per ulteriori informazioni sui servizi descrizione linguaggio WSDL (Web), vedere la specifica http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeXmlBinding"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inizializza una nuova istanza di <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeXmlBinding"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart"></xref> to which the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeXmlBinding"></xref> applies.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene o imposta il nome del <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart"> </xref> a cui il <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeXmlBinding"> </xref> si applica.

trans-unit.source: The default value is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Il valore predefinito è una stringa vuota ("").
